title: Bill Withers - Still Bill (2015) [96-24 HD FLAC]
description:
Still Bill is the second studio album by Bill Withers, released in 1972. It includes two hit singles: "Lean on Me", which is number 205 on Rolling Stone's 500 Greatest Songs of All Time and went to number 1 on the Billboard pop and R&B charts in summer of 1972; and "Use Me", which went to number two on the same charts in fall of 1972.
